test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] == [2, 3, 4]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 4
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
  ?  +++       +++
test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6, 8, 10] == [4, 6, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 4
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8]
  + [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
